code: public void setKey(int key) {     this.key = key. }
public void setValue(int[] value) {     this.value = value. }

code: /**  * returns record size when serialized in bytes  *  * @return size in bytes  */ public int getSerializedSize() {     return (2 + this.value.length) * 4. }

@Override public String toString() {     String result = "( " + this.key + " / ".     for (int i = 0. i < value.length. i++) {         result = result + value[i] + " ".     }     return result + ")". }
